                <div class="comment-gravatar"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/0684c764a3a991a15f597e7babf153af?s=65&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2Flinuxundich.de%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fyoko_lui%2Fimages%2Fgravatar_default.png%3Fs%3D65&amp;r=X' class='avatar avatar-65 photo' height='65' width='65' /></div>
		<div class="comment-body">
		<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
		<cite class="fn">White Rabbit</cite><br/>
		<a href="http://linuxundich.de/gnu-linux/pc-funkfernbedienung-x10-unter-ubuntu-mit-lirc/#comment-6305">
			20. Januar 2010 um 19:47 Uhr</a>		</div><!-- .comment-meta .commentmetadata -->

		<p>ich sehe gerade:<br />
htpc:~/.mythtv $ cat lircrc<br />
# LIRCRC Auto Generated by Mythbuntu Lirc Generator<br />
# Author(s): Mario Limonciello, Nick Fox<br />
# Created for use with Mythbuntu<br />
[...]<br />
begin<br />
    remote = Medion_X10_Remote_Control<br />
    prog = mythtv<br />
    button = down<br />
    config = Down<br />
    repeat = 0<br />
    delay = 0<br />
end<br />
[...]<br />
stimmt also schon so</p>

		
